Can I add multiple association labels in a batch association creation action by including multiple “types”? i.e., would the following be allowed?

```curl --request POST \
  --url <https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/associations///batch/labels/archive> \
  --header 'authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN' \
  --header 'content-type: application/json' \
  --data '{
  "inputs": [
    {
      "types": [
        {
          "associationCategory": "HubSpot_DEFINED",
          "associationTypeId": 0
        },
        {
          "associationCategory": "HubSpot_DEFINED",
          "associationTypeId": 1
        }
      ],
      "from": {
        "id": "string"
      },
      "to": {
        "id": "string"
      }
    }
  ]
}'```
